- üì• **modusa I/O**
- ‚ôªÔ∏è **modusa Engines**

---

## Installation

> modusa is under active development. You can install the latest version via:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/meluron/modusa.git
cd modusa
pdm install
```

---

## Tests

```bash
pytest tests/
```

